          "thinking": "Wall area: perimeter = 2 × (6 + 1.2) = 14.4 m. Wall area = 14.4 × 2.4 = 34.56 m².\n\nSubtract openings: three doors ≈ 3 × (0.76 × 2.0) = 4.56 m². One window ≈ 1.2 × 1.0 = 1.2 m². Net ≈ 28.8 m².\n\nTwo coats → 57.6 m². Coverage ~12 m²/L → 4.8 L. Recommend 5 L can.",
