          "type": "text",
          "text": "You'll need about **4.8 litres**, so buy a 5 L can.\n\n- Net wall area: ≈ 28.8 m² (34.6 m² minus doors and window)\n- Two coats: ≈ 57.6 m²\n- At ~12 m² per litre: ≈ 4.8 L",
